United Basalt of Mauritius Drops Most in 5 Weeks on Lower Profit

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-05-13T09:19:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-13/united-basalt-of-mauritius-drops-most-in-5-weeks-on-lower-profit.html
United Basalt Products Ltd., a
Mauritian building materials manufacturer and retailer, declined
the most in five weeks after it reported third-quarter profit
slumped 68 percent.  The stock retreated 0.7 percent, or 1 rupee, to 144 rupees
at 1:06 p.m., in  Port Louis , its biggest intraday decline since
April 7.  Net income dropped to 17.7 million rupees ($637,837) from
55.3 million rupees the same period a year earlier, according to
a statement published on the bourseâ€™s website after the end of
